<p>This Privacy policy between OYOYO App of the Oyoyo Wellness Centre, Society for Public Health and Social Development located at 24, 461 Road, Federal Housing Lugbe, Abuja  (SPHSD) and you, constitutes our commitment to your privacy on our application, records, websites, social media platforms and premises. We are very keen on your privacy. This document therefore discloses how your information is gathered and disseminated for the purposes of Hypertension prevention, management and control across various African countries.</p>
<h3>The Data we collect about you</h3>
<p>Personal data or information means any information about an individual from which that person can be identified. It does not include where the identity has been removed. We may collect, use, store and transfer the following personal data about you:<br>
Identity Data: First name, last name, username, title<br>
Contact data: Email address and health centre<br>
Technical data: Internet Protocol (IP) address, your login data, browser type and version time zone setting and location, browser plug-in types and versions, operating system and platform and other technology on the devices you use to access this website.<br>
