<h3>How your personal data is collected?</h3>
<p>Direct interactions: You provide us with your data by filling them in the app directly or by giving permission to other app users like the Blood Pressure commanders and Non-physician health workers to record your information in the various communities and health centres. This also includes personal data you provide when you agree for marketing information to be sent to you.</p>
Automated technologies or interactions:  As you interact with the app, we may automatically collect technical data about your equipment.<br>
